I find it distasteful that other players can be so selfish that they think they have the right to bother people they don't know for buffs using the tell system.  If anyone sends me a tell asking for advice on something, help with a CR/epic fight, or pretty much anything else I am happy to talk to them.  If someone sends me a tell begging, be it for KEI, platinum, equipment, I ignore them. /shrug..<br>
<br>
I don't consider it distasteful to refuse to interact with irritating people in a computer game.  I refuse to interact with irritating people in RL.<br>
