3) Drop by PoK and drop a few pps for the buff.<br>
<br>
1 means less AA/hour, and AA/hour is the name of this game. We are Pavlov's little dogs, salivating at each ding. Sometimes we roleplay a lil. Ok, I am a cynic old bastard.<br>
<br>
2 means nagging on your friends. It probably doesn't get to them as much as it gets to me. But I find it wearying to ask people on my friends list for rebuffs every three hours. A quick break for coffee, toilet and PoK Buffing System is better.<br>
<br>
